# Articles

Stay up to date with the latest insights, tutorials, and thoughts on software development from the Sibylline Software team.

{% if collections.articles.length > 0 %}
<div class="articles-list">
  {% for article in collections.articles %}
  <article class="article-preview">
    <h2><a href="{{ article.url }}">{{ article.data.title }}</a></h2>
    <div class="article-meta">
      <time datetime="{{ article.date | htmlDateString }}">{{ article.date | readableDate }}</time>
      {% if article.data.tags %}
      <div class="article-tags">
        {% for tag in article.data.tags %}
          {% if tag != "articles" %}
          <span class="tag">{{ tag }}</span>
          {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
    {% if article.data.description %}
    <p class="article-excerpt">{{ article.data.description }}</p>
    {% endif %}
    <a href="{{ article.url }}" class="read-more">Read more â†’</a>
  </article>
  {% endfor %}
</div>

